init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Men everywhere start to internally freak out.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The days of coasting on the "fatherhood credit" are over.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Many have speculated that this new era of fatherhood will rival the renaissance.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It will be the catalyst for a new age.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Maybe they won't need a ranking system at all.
